  "instructions": [
    "preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "season snapper fillets with oregano, salt, and black pepper.",
    "brush grill grates with olive oil to prevent sticking.",
    "grill snapper fillets for 4-5 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "while snapper is cooking, grill slices of red onion, red bell pepper, and zucchini for 3-4 minutes per side, or until tender.",
    "transfer cooked vegetables to a plate and brush with olive oil.",
    "chop parsley and mix with garlic, lemon juice, and a pinch of salt.",
    "brush snapper fillets with chimichurri and grill for an additional 1-2 minutes per side, or until heated through.",
    "serve snapper on a bed of grilled vegetables, topped with a dollop of chimichurri, grilled scallions, and a sprinkle of parsley."
  ],
